The paper focuses on combining nonparametric topic models with Auto-Encoding Variational Bayes (AEVB) using neural networks for inference. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
